IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User b.leonhardt.pacheco@gmail.com
TLSType IMAPS
SystemCertificates yes
PassCmd "pass token/b.leonhardt.pacheco@gmail.com/mbsync"

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail-inbox
Far :gmail-remote:INBOX
Near :gmail-local:INBOX
SyncState *
Create Near
Remove None
Expunge None

Channel gmail-labels
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * !INBOX !"[Gmail]/*" !"All Mail" !"Drafts" !"Trash"
SyncState *
Create Both
Remove Both
Expunge None

Channel gmail-defaults
Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/"
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "All Mail" "Drafts" "Trash"
SyncState *
Create Near
Remove None
Expunge None

Group gmail
Channel gmail-inbox
Channel gmail-labels
Channel gmail-defaults
